S.FORM: O Ci'i Pintu (Holam: 記憶拼圖, ira ko Pintu no ca'emotan) cacey kamoko'ay a tilifi ega i Taywan. Misanga' Pipahosoan to tilifi no Yen-cu-min ci ina to tilifi ega. Mipasadak to 2015 a miheca saka 12 a folad saka 26 a romi'ad 9:00 dadaya. Mianingaya a patingso^ Panai : Low Fu-mey Inaan no Panai : Ye Hung Nayaw: Low Ca-un
